data.description: This custom home was just completed July of 2014, like new construction without the wait. 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and a spacious study, all on one level. High end finishes and construction include high impact hurricane windows, Icynene insulation, custom wood cabinetry, granite throughout, and rich hand scraped eucalyptus wood floors with beautiful tile in baths and laundry (no carpet). Bright and open floor plan with 8' doors, and 10' and 12' ceilings appointed with hand hewn solid pine beams in the great room, master bedroom and lanai. The great room has a 16 foot window wall opening to the salt water pool with large lanai and cabana that feature beautiful cypress ceilings and paver decking. This large entertaining space privately backs up to lush green space. The open kitchen is equipped with Electrolux stainless appliances, wine cooler and walk in pantry. The master suite has his and her closets, a beautiful wood accent wall, and french doors leading to the cabana. An oversized 3 car garage with epoxy floors and will house your vehicles plus storage needs. Blackburn Estates on the Bay is a gated waterfront community of only 22 custom homes and is walking distance or short bike ride to the beach, shops and restaurants. Convenient to US 41 and Hwy 681, which means only 1 traffic light to I-75.  Low HOA, no CDD fees.
